<br>
Fair enough.<br>
<br>
&quot;1) Their 50% slow has no Magic+ stat in the spdat file, meaning it will be easier to land than any other slow.&quot;<br>
<br>
Noone really knows how many Raid mobs are out there that, after Malo/Mala/Tash/Occ/Scent/whatever I'm leaving out would still be Not hittable by the standard 80% slow (?+25 MR?), but would be hittable by 50% slow (+0MR).  Could very well be a nitch for the lvl 60 BL; also a decent thing for just exping.<br>
<br>
&quot;2) Assuming the trend that has been maintained up to 55 continues, their level 60 pet will be level 60. Toss a few resistance buffs, a 300 mana 1250 heal, and &quot;/pet hold&quot; in and you've got the best pet damage there is, probably outdamaging most PCs at 60 (plus the beastlord's damage).&quot;<br>
<br>
Well, being that a) pet pathing in too many of the zones sucks ass, and b) &quot;higher damage than most PCs&quot; without any type of evade skill (FD/evade/jolt) + nukes / dots / *slows* is instant death, specially to a class that gets to wear that every so protecting *leather* class armors; I don't see pets as a Raid lvl item.<br>
<br>
&quot;3) They have a few other buffs that seem as though they would stack with everything.&quot;<br>
<br>
Well, that would be a Raid lvl item, assuming the buffs are HP/ac/resist buffs, and not stupid shit.<br>
<br>
&quot;They might end up being totally useless, but we won't know for a while. Besides, if they do end composing the cheer team on high end raids, there's always room to improve them.&quot;<br>
<br>
&lt;insert standard coment about paying for beta&gt;,&lt;insert standard comment about fools trusting VI to do the right thing&gt;,&lt;insert standard comment noting how long it takes VI to correct class imbalances, once they finally acnoledge them&gt;<br>
<br>
Weither you think I'm bitter, or just realistic depends on how long and how hard VI has had you bent over the barrel.  Are you a relativly new player, since the time they learned about K-Y?  Or are you an old foogy, who remebers  the days and days of removing the spinters and glass shards from your ass, after VI got done with you?<br>
<br>
Ninen of Saryrn<br>
